```python
import pandas as pd

df_meas = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1","B1","B1","B2","B2","B2"],
    "day":   [1,2,3, 1,2,3],
    "temp":  [37.0, 37.2, 37.1, 36.8, 36.7, 36.6]
})
df_batch = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1","B2"],
    "target_temp": [37.0, 36.8]
})
display(df_meas, df_batch)
```

```python
df_merged = df_meas.merge(df_batch, how='left', on='batch')
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted = df_merged.sort_values(by=['batch','day'], ascending=True)
batch_feat = df_merged_sorted.groupby('batch').agg(
    temp_mean = ('temp', 'mean'),
    temp_last = ('temp', 'last'),
).reset_index()
display(batch_feat)
batch_feat = batch_feat.merge(df_batch, on='batch', how='left')
batch_feat['is_cold'] = batch_feat['temp_mean'] < batch_feat['target_temp']
display(batch_feat)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(6,4))
ax.plot(df_meas[df_meas['batch']=='B1']['day'], df_meas[df_meas['batch']=='B1']['temp'])
ax.plot(df_meas[df_meas['batch']=='B2']['day'], df_meas[df_meas['batch']=='B2']['temp'])
ax.axhline(df_batch[df_batch['batch']=='B1']['target_temp'].item(), color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
ax.axhline(df_batch[df_batch['batch']=='B2']['target_temp'].item(), color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
ax.set_title("Temperature Trend by Batch")
ax.set_xlabel("day")
ax.set_ylabel("temp")
```
